      <title>欧洲央行行长拉加德敦促欧洲进行谈判，而不是在贸易问题上采取报复措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/ecb-s-lagarde-urges-europe-to-negotiate-not-retaliate-on-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，如果欧盟与美国就潜在的贸易关税进行谈判，而不是立即采取反制措施，欧盟可能会处于更有利的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/ecb-s-lagarde-urges-europe-to-negotiate-not-retaliate-on-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 05:36:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收购竞争加剧 七喜公司保证金收购飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/seven-i-margin-buying-soar-as-takeover-race-intensifies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者越来越多地希望创始家族能迅速收购这家日本零售巨头，因此他们使用借入资金购买 Seven &amp; i Holdings Co. 股票的数量达到至少十年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/seven-i-margin-buying-soar-as-takeover-race-intensifies</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 05:26:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强导致印尼股市吸引力下降，外国人纷纷逃离印尼股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/foreigners-flee-indonesian-stocks-as-strong-dollar-dents-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强削弱了新兴市场资产的吸引力，外国投资者对印尼股票的警惕性日益提高，股票资金已连续 15 个交易日外流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/foreigners-flee-indonesian-stocks-as-strong-dollar-dents-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 05:08:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>喜力计划在迪拜建造海湾地区第一家大型啤酒厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/heineken-plans-gulf-s-first-large-scale-brewery-in-dubai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜即将迎来海湾地区第一家大型啤酒厂，喜力啤酒公司 (Heineken NV) 的合资企业计划开始在迪拜酋长国生产受欢迎的啤酒品牌，这对于一个长期以来对酒精销售和消费实行严格限制的地区来说是一个里程碑式的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/heineken-plans-gulf-s-first-large-scale-brewery-in-dubai</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 05:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东欧央行已成为全球最大的黄金买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/gold-prices-tempt-eastern-europe-central-banks-seeking-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年早些时候，捷克共和国央行行长飞往伦敦，查看存放在针线街下方英格兰银行混凝土金库中的大量金条。]]></description>
