    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德退出后，亿万富翁 Grifols 家族的困境成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/billionaire-grifols-family-s-woes-in-focus-after-brookfield-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于西班牙亿万富翁 Grifols 家族来说，布鲁克菲尔德资产管理公司 (Brookfield Asset Management) 将陷入困境的同名公司私有化的计划是一种摆脱市场关注、扭转局面的方法。该家族将一家采血公司打造成了全球最大的医疗财富之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/billionaire-grifols-family-s-woes-in-focus-after-brookfield-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>夏季临近，澳大利亚山火风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/australia-facing-elevated-risk-of-wildfires-as-summer-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据季节性预测，今年夏天，澳大利亚的一些主要葡萄酒产区以及大片牧场和地区城镇面临着更高的野火风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/australia-facing-elevated-risk-of-wildfires-as-summer-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 04:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪将斯里兰卡列入信用评级上调审查名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/moody-s-places-sri-lanka-on-review-for-credit-rating-upgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于斯里兰卡即将完成美元债券重组，穆迪评级正在审查斯里兰卡的主权信用评级，以确定其是否有望上调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/moody-s-places-sri-lanka-on-review-for-credit-rating-upgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 04:27:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国考虑对中国芯片实施进一步限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-28/us-weighs-additional-china-chip-curbs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，拜登政府正在考虑对向中国销售半导体设备和人工智能内存芯片采取更多限制措施。消息人士称，此举没有达到之前考虑的一些更严格的措施。彭博社的 Debby Wu 报道。

（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-28/us-weighs-additional-china-chip-curbs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 04:09:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
